 → <code>KQueueSocketChannel</code> </li> </ul> <p>Because the native transport is not part of the Netty core, you need to pull the <code>netty-transport-native-kqueue</code> as a dependency in your Maven <code>pom.xml</code>:</p> <div class=\"highlight highlight-text-xml notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"  &lt;dependencies&gt;     &lt;dependency&gt;       &lt;groupId&gt;io.netty&lt;/groupId&gt;       &lt;artifactId&gt;netty-transport-native-kqueue&lt;/artifactId&gt;       &lt;version&gt;${project.version}&lt;/version&gt;       &lt;classifier&gt;osx-x86_64&lt;/classifier&gt;     &lt;/\n---\nve overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"  &lt;dependencies&gt;     &lt;dependency&gt;       &lt;groupId&gt;io.netty&lt;/groupId&gt;       &lt;artifactId&gt;netty-transport-native-kqueue&lt;/artifactId&gt;       &lt;version&gt;${project.version}&lt;/version&gt;       &lt;classifier&gt;osx-x86_64&lt;/classifier&gt;     &lt;/dependency&gt;     ...   &lt;/dependencies&gt;\"><pre>  &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\">dependencies</span>&gt;&#x000A;    &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\">dependency</span>&gt;&#x000A;      &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\">groupId</span>&gt;io.netty&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\">groupId</span>&gt;&#x000A;      &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\">artifactId</span>&gt;netty-transport-native-kqueue&lt;/<span class=\"pl-ent\">artifactId</span>&gt;&#x000A;      &lt;<span class=\"pl-ent\">version</span>&g\n---\nki/Native-transports\">here!</a> </div> <div class=\"row\"> <div class=\"col-md-9\"> <div id=\"wiki-body\" class=\"gollum-markdown-content\">               <div class=\"markdown-body\">                 <p>Netty provides the following platform specific JNI transports:</p> <ul> <li>Linux (since 4.0.16)</li> <li>MacOS/BSD (since 4.1.11)</li> </ul> <p>These JNI transports add features specific to a particular platform, generate less garbage, and generally improve performance when compared to the NIO based transport.</p> <div class=\"markdown-heading\"> <h2 class=\"heading-element\" id=\"wiki-h2-0\">Using the native transports</h2> <a id=\"user-content-using-the-native-transports\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Using the native transports\" href=\"#using-the-native-transports\"><svg data-component=\"Octicon\" \n---\nURL https://netty.io/4.2/api/io/netty/channel/kqueue/package-summary.html\n<!DOCTYPE HTML> <!-- NewPage --> <html lang=\"en\"> <head> <!-- Generated by javadoc (11.0.31) on Mon Jun 01 23:06:50 PDT 2026 --> <title>io.netty.channel.kqueue (Netty API Reference (4.2.15.Final))</title> <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\"> <meta name=\"dc.created\" content=\"2026-06-01\"> <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"io.netty.channel.kqueue package\"> <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../../../../stylesheet.css\" title=\"Style\"> <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../../../../jquery/jquery-ui.min.css\" title=\"Style\"> <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../../../../jquery-ui.overrides.css\" t\n---\nURL https://netty.io/4.2/api/io/netty/channel/kqueue/KQueue.html\n<!DOCTYPE HTML> <!-- NewPage --> <html lang=\"en\"> <head> <!-- Generated by javadoc (11.0.31) on Mon Jun 01 23:06:50 PDT 2026 --> <title>KQueue (Netty API Reference (4.2.15.Final))</title> <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\"> <meta name=\"dc.created\" content=\"2026-06-01\"> <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"io.netty.channel.kqueue.KQueue class\"> <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"isAvailable()\"> <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"ensureAvailability()\"> <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"unavailabilityCause()\"> <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"isTcpFastOpenClientSideAvailable()\"> <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"isTcpFast\n---\n=\"colFirst\"><code>static void</code></td> <th class=\"colSecond\" scope=\"row\"><code><span class=\"memberNameLink\"><a href=\"#ensureAvailability()\">ensureAvailability</a></span>()</code></th> <td class=\"colLast\"> <div class=\"block\">Ensure that <a href=\"https://netty.io/wiki/native-transports.html\"><code>netty-transport-native-kqueue</code></a> is  available.</div> </td> </tr> <tr id=\"i1\" class=\"rowColor\"> <td class=\"colFirst\"><code>static boolean</code></td> <th class=\"colSecond\" scope=\"row\"><code><span class=\"memberNameLink\"><a href=\"#isAvailable()\">isAvailable</a></span>()</code></th> <td class=\"colLast\"> <div class=\"block\">Returns <code>true</code> if and only if the <a href=\"https://netty.io/wiki/native-transports.html\"><code>  netty-transport-native-kqueue</code></a> is available.</div> </\n---\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782470650176}]}
